name: 07 Libra
description: 07 Virgo is the 7th piece in the ‘Origins Mini’ collection, in correlation with my ‘Origins’ Collection on Rarible. The ‘Origins Mini’ collection has over 100 unique designs to be minted, each with a different rarity ranging from 1/1 to 50 editions. The first 12 pieces in the collection representing the Zodiac guardians will each have 10 editions.
